WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

2
00:00:10.060 --> 00:00:14.640
This may not mean anything to you,

3
00:00:16.270 --> 00:00:18.160
but it's different for me.

4
00:00:19.360 --> 00:00:22.850
Even holding your hand, 
even just touching you...

5
00:00:23.790 --> 00:00:26.160
makes my heart ache so badly.

6
00:00:26.790 --> 00:00:30.500
H-Hananoi-kun, what's wro—

7
00:00:31.470 --> 00:00:34.710
<i>His heart is beating so fast!</i>

8
00:00:35.260 --> 00:00:37.260
<i>Does he always get like this?</i>

9
00:00:38.380 --> 00:00:42.060
<i>Every time he's... with me?</i>

10
00:00:44.130 --> 00:00:48.640
I'm not the kind of person you think I am.

11
00:00:49.390 --> 00:00:52.090
Really, I'm always...

12
00:00:52.490 --> 00:00:55.480
Hananoi-kun, are you sure you're feeling—

13
00:00:58.220 --> 00:00:59.560
Hotaru-chan.

14
00:01:01.750 --> 00:01:03.180
I <i>really</i> like you.

15
00:01:08.120 --> 00:01:09.360
H-Hana...

16
00:01:10.150 --> 00:01:11.460
Hananoi-kun, wait!

17
00:01:25.250 --> 00:01:28.180
H-Hananoi-kun, are you okay?

18
00:01:28.180 --> 00:01:29.520
Y-You're burning up!

19
00:01:33.270 --> 00:01:34.620
That scared me...

20
00:01:35.800 --> 00:01:39.340
He must felt bad all day
 and just didn't tell me.

21
00:01:39.340 --> 00:01:42.860
I knew you'd get sick always waiting
for me in the cold like that.

22
00:01:44.570 --> 00:01:46.240
Why didn't you say something?

23
00:01:46.870 --> 00:01:50.110
<i>I want to spend every second I can with you.</i>

24
00:01:50.730 --> 00:01:52.840
I-I need to call his family!

25
00:01:56.390 --> 00:01:58.030
<i>I had no idea.</i>

26
00:01:58.630 --> 00:02:02.900
<i>Between love and friendship, I didn't realize
</i>liking<i> someone meant something so different...</i>

27
00:02:04.180 --> 00:02:07.460
<i>But this is... It's nothing like those things.</i>

28
00:02:08.230 --> 00:02:13.940
H-Hello. Um, Hananoi-kun fainted. 
Could you please come right away?

29
00:02:14.700 --> 00:02:17.360
Yes. Thank you very much.

30
00:02:23.760 --> 00:02:26.260
<i>I still remember the way he felt...</i>

31
00:02:27.530 --> 00:02:34.050
<i>Am I really going to be able to experience
 feelings like that one day?</i>

32
00:04:05.390 --> 00:04:11.850
Episode 3

33
00:04:05.390 --> 00:04:11.850
Our First Christmas

34
00:04:05.890 --> 00:04:07.820
Hey, Big Sis!

35
00:04:08.350 --> 00:04:10.270
It's time for dinner!

36
00:04:10.970 --> 00:04:12.090
I don't want any.

37
00:04:12.090 --> 00:04:13.240
Huh?!

38
00:04:13.240 --> 00:04:16.190
<i>You</i> don't want dinner? What's wrong?

39
00:04:16.410 --> 00:04:20.810
I don't feel like I deserve it right now.

40
00:04:22.780 --> 00:04:24.160
Don't overdo it!

41
00:04:24.160 --> 00:04:28.740
Hey! Don't let good food to go waste 
over your petty guilt.

42
00:04:28.740 --> 00:04:29.940
You're right.

43
00:04:34.850 --> 00:04:39.610
<i>But the way I made him look... 
How can I apologize for that?</i>

44
00:04:40.470 --> 00:04:44.130
<i>What am I gonna do?!</i>

45
00:04:47.550 --> 00:04:56.560
December 23rd

46
00:04:47.550 --> 00:04:56.560
I'm really sorry about yesterday. It was thoughtless of me
 to ask to kiss you to see if I liked you. I regret saying that.
How are you doing now? Please message me once you're feeling better.

47
00:04:59.820 --> 00:05:03.070
I want to spend Christmas Eve with you

48
00:05:03.200 --> 00:05:07.360
Okay, then I'll give you my answer 
after our date. Is that okay?

49
00:05:07.360 --> 00:05:08.440
Yeah.

50
00:05:10.410 --> 00:05:12.500
This'll be new for me.

51
00:05:12.500 --> 00:05:15.720
I've always spent Christmas with my family.

52
00:05:15.720 --> 00:05:17.150
Every year?

53
00:05:17.150 --> 00:05:20.740
My little sister does figure skating.

54
00:05:20.740 --> 00:05:23.150
She always does a show on Christmas Eve.

55
00:05:23.150 --> 00:05:25.300
We all go to cheer her on.

56
00:05:25.300 --> 00:05:29.600
She's really something! She gets dressed 
up like a sparkly little princess.

57
00:05:30.050 --> 00:05:31.560
A princess?

58
00:05:32.440 --> 00:05:34.640
Don't you ever hang out with friends?

59
00:05:36.660 --> 00:05:39.860
They all end up going on dates or trips.

60
00:05:40.390 --> 00:05:44.610
Yeah? Then I'll do my best to escort <i>you</i>.

61
00:05:45.910 --> 00:05:48.450
I'm looking forward to it.

62
00:05:46.700 --> 00:05:49.110
I want to spend Christmas Eve with you

63
00:05:52.490 --> 00:05:55.870
December 24th

64
00:05:52.700 --> 00:05:55.870
<i>Today's the last day 
of our trial dating period.</i>

65
00:05:56.690 --> 00:06:01.890
<i>If nothing else happens, then tomorrow
we'll just become... strangers?</i>

66
00:06:02.250 --> 00:06:06.010
December 24th

67
00:06:03.190 --> 00:06:06.270
<i>He must not be answering because he's sick.</i>

68
00:06:06.980 --> 00:06:08.910
<i>But he always responds so quickly...</i>

69
00:06:09.390 --> 00:06:14.010
<i>Ah, maybe he's given up on me now.</i>

70
00:06:14.300 --> 00:06:19.530
<i>I was basically toying with 
Hananoi-kun's feelings, after all.</i>

71
00:06:19.530 --> 00:06:21.970
Huh? You're still here, Hotaru?

72
00:06:22.870 --> 00:06:25.530
Mom and everyone already 
left for the skating rink.

73
00:06:25.530 --> 00:06:27.860
Are you going there now, Kagari?

74
00:06:27.860 --> 00:06:30.460
My club is having a Christmas 
party, so I'm gonna pass.

75
00:06:30.820 --> 00:06:32.880
Okay, don't forget to lock up.

76
00:06:38.660 --> 00:06:42.750
<i>You never thought about 
how I felt, Hotaru-chan.</i>

77
00:06:44.900 --> 00:06:47.010
<i>It's happening all over again.</i>

78
00:06:47.010 --> 00:06:49.630
<i>Will this all end without me 
ever expressing my feelings?</i>

79
00:06:50.110 --> 00:06:52.910
<i>I really want to apologize to Hananoi-kun.</i>

80
00:06:52.910 --> 00:06:55.340
<i>I haven't even given him an answer yet!</i>

81
00:06:57.140 --> 00:06:59.340
<i>I should at least try calling him.</i>

82
00:07:00.220 --> 00:07:00.880
What?!

83
00:07:02.170 --> 00:07:04.270
Yes? Hello?

84
00:07:10.530 --> 00:07:12.660
Ice Skating Rink

85
00:07:11.450 --> 00:07:13.980
Hotaru! You're late!

86
00:07:15.190 --> 00:07:19.740
Here's the... sewing kit... you asked for.

87
00:07:20.040 --> 00:07:24.120
Sorry to drag you out here. 
Her costume ripped.

88
00:07:23.330 --> 00:07:25.910
Come on, Mom! Hurry, hurry!

89
00:07:28.110 --> 00:07:30.040
Yes! It's perfect!

90
00:07:30.040 --> 00:07:34.440
Mm-hmm, I hate to say it myself, 
but my work this year is a masterpiece!

91
00:07:35.010 --> 00:07:37.000
You look so pretty, Tomo-chan!

92
00:07:37.000 --> 00:07:39.700
And today, I'm the star!

93
00:07:39.700 --> 00:07:42.070
Yes! The prettiest princess in the world!

94
00:07:43.200 --> 00:07:46.310
Hotaru, I thought you had plans. 
Is everything all right?

95
00:07:46.310 --> 00:07:50.570
Yeah. My friend just caught a cold,
and I haven't heard anything since.

96
00:07:50.570 --> 00:07:53.340
Oh my. Want to stay and watch, then?

97
00:07:55.180 --> 00:07:56.820
I guess so.

98
00:08:02.130 --> 00:08:06.740
It'll be okay. How about we go out for 
something you like for dinner later?

99
00:08:07.550 --> 00:08:09.840
Sure. Thanks.

100
00:08:12.260 --> 00:08:16.510
Christmas Ice Show

101
00:08:12.270 --> 00:08:16.060
<i>I guess it turned out to be 
just another normal Christmas.</i>

102
00:08:16.510 --> 00:08:17.760
Hananoi-kun

103
00:08:16.510 --> 00:08:17.760
Hananoi-kun

104
00:08:16.510 --> 00:08:17.760
Hananoi-kun

105
00:08:16.510 --> 00:08:17.760
Hananoi-kun

106
00:08:16.510 --> 00:08:17.760
Missed Call

107
00:08:16.510 --> 00:08:17.760
Missed Call

108
00:08:16.510 --> 00:08:17.760
Missed Call

109
00:08:18.000 --> 00:08:21.530
<i>Hananoi-kun?! When did I get 
all these notifications?</i>

110
00:08:24.540 --> 00:08:26.250
H-Hello?

111
00:08:26.250 --> 00:08:27.210
<i>Hotaru-chan?!</i>

112
00:08:29.170 --> 00:08:31.010
<i>Where are you right now?</i>

113
00:08:31.030 --> 00:08:34.280
Christmas Ice Show

114
00:08:31.350 --> 00:08:35.690
Uh, um... Sorry. I'm at the skating rink.

115
00:08:34.760 --> 00:08:36.050
I found you!

116
00:08:54.750 --> 00:08:56.310
Oh! Hananoi-kun!

117
00:08:56.780 --> 00:08:58.250
What are you doing here?

118
00:08:58.250 --> 00:09:01.120
I called... but you didn't answer.

119
00:09:01.560 --> 00:09:07.140
I remembered you said you go to see 
your sister skate every Christmas.

120
00:09:07.750 --> 00:09:11.960
So I searched for rinks
with Christmas shows...

121
00:09:12.470 --> 00:09:17.790
And this was the only place near
your house hosting anything like that.

122
00:09:17.790 --> 00:09:19.060
<i>Talk about commitment!</i>

123
00:09:19.720 --> 00:09:23.860
What a surprise. I didn't think 
I'd get to see you today.

124
00:09:23.860 --> 00:09:27.780
I'm sorry! I've been in bed 
and just saw your message...

125
00:09:30.850 --> 00:09:32.130
Hotaru-chan?

126
00:09:33.110 --> 00:09:37.550
What? What is this? I feel so drained.

127
00:09:38.140 --> 00:09:43.380
I think it's because I've been so consumed
with worry and stress the past few days.

128
00:09:43.910 --> 00:09:46.910
But seeing you, I feel so relieved now.

129
00:09:48.310 --> 00:09:49.650
So very relieved.

130
00:09:50.660 --> 00:09:52.440
I'm so glad.

131
00:09:53.280 --> 00:09:57.150
I'm so glad I got to see 
you again, Hananoi-kun.

132
00:09:58.150 --> 00:09:59.880
Wonderful, wonderful!

133
00:09:59.880 --> 00:10:01.410
You did great!

134
00:10:08.690 --> 00:10:10.920
Here. Is this okay?

135
00:10:10.920 --> 00:10:15.070
Y-Yeah. Sorry you had to see me like that.

136
00:10:16.030 --> 00:10:18.410
It's my fault, isn't it?

137
00:10:18.810 --> 00:10:22.240
I'm really sorry I scared you the other day!

138
00:10:22.650 --> 00:10:25.680
You even called my grandmother for me...

139
00:10:25.680 --> 00:10:28.010
O-Oh, no, that wasn't it.

140
00:10:28.010 --> 00:10:32.560
I'm sorry the thoughtless things 
I said I hurt you so much!

141
00:10:34.070 --> 00:10:37.690
It's not the first time
I've done something like that...

142
00:10:38.090 --> 00:10:41.980
Not been able to understand
the way someone else felt, I mean.

143
00:10:41.980 --> 00:10:43.960
She was a good friend of mine,

144
00:10:43.950 --> 00:10:47.330
Roasted Green Tea

145
00:10:44.870 --> 00:10:46.420
but I hurt her.

146
00:10:47.770 --> 00:10:53.340
And before I had a chance
 to say I was sorry, we'd drifted apart.

147
00:10:54.070 --> 00:10:57.950
I was worried the same thing 
would happen with you.

148
00:10:59.180 --> 00:11:04.210
I see. It sounds like that really upset you.

149
00:11:05.190 --> 00:11:08.780
I-I'm sorry! I didn't mean to bring that up.

150
00:11:08.780 --> 00:11:12.670
That's right! I still need to give
 you a proper answer, don't I?

151
00:11:12.670 --> 00:11:14.830
Uh... Um...

152
00:11:17.690 --> 00:11:19.060
It's okay.

153
00:11:19.450 --> 00:11:22.500
You can give me your answer 
whenever you want.

154
00:11:30.160 --> 00:11:31.430
But more importantly,

155
00:11:31.430 --> 00:11:36.510
if you're willing to make up with me, 
then would you care to go on our date now?

156
00:11:38.130 --> 00:11:43.880
No matter what your answer is, 
I want to make this a special day for you.

157
00:11:43.880 --> 00:11:45.570
I've been planning it for ages.

158
00:11:51.660 --> 00:11:54.580
Ah, I almost forgot.

159
00:11:54.580 --> 00:11:56.970
I don't want to make the same mistake again.

160
00:11:57.310 --> 00:12:02.080
Starting today, unless I have your 
permission, I won't... touch you.

161
00:12:06.110 --> 00:12:08.830
You sure can be a handful, Hananoi-kun.

162
00:12:11.820 --> 00:12:13.560
I finally got you to smile.

163
00:12:25.760 --> 00:12:28.370
<i>I've learned so much this month.</i>

164
00:12:28.370 --> 00:12:32.090
<i>Hananoi-kun is kind. He tries hard...</i>

165
00:12:32.780 --> 00:12:37.230
<i>Maybe too hard. And sometimes he
does things I'd never expect.</i>

166
00:12:37.660 --> 00:12:41.230
<i>He likes books.
He's good at helping me study.</i>

167
00:12:42.060 --> 00:12:45.730
<i>He always slows down to walk at my pace.</i>

168
00:12:46.680 --> 00:12:48.200
<i>Hananoi-kun is...</i>

169
00:12:50.330 --> 00:12:52.800
Everyone sure was surprised.

170
00:12:53.460 --> 00:12:54.380
Yeah.

171
00:12:55.210 --> 00:12:59.250
Would you mind if I chaperoned 
Hotaru-chan until this evening?

172
00:13:00.160 --> 00:13:03.760
You have my word that
 you have no cause for concern.

173
00:13:03.760 --> 00:13:06.250
And I promise to bring 
her home safely tonight.

174
00:13:07.060 --> 00:13:09.560
Today's a very important day for me.

175
00:13:10.360 --> 00:13:12.570
I would like to spend the 
rest of it with her.

176
00:13:13.880 --> 00:13:17.200
<i>They totally thought he was my boyfriend.</i>

177
00:13:17.930 --> 00:13:21.800
<i>That isn't exactly wrong, though, 
so it's fine... I guess.</i>

178
00:13:23.650 --> 00:13:24.380
Hmm?

179
00:13:24.650 --> 00:13:28.880
Hananoi-kun, are you really 
feeling better now?

180
00:13:28.880 --> 00:13:30.670
Yeah. Totally.

181
00:13:30.670 --> 00:13:33.910
After resting for two days,
I actually feel great.

182
00:13:38.790 --> 00:13:44.210
There's only one December 24th,
so I wanted to be with you.

183
00:13:44.670 --> 00:13:48.380
Remember? I said I'd 
make it a special day for you.

184
00:13:48.380 --> 00:13:52.930
That's really nice of you, 
but where are we going this late?

185
00:13:57.410 --> 00:13:59.290
Wow!

186
00:14:00.450 --> 00:14:05.260
I didn't know the amusement park was 
like this during winter! I had no idea!

187
00:14:05.980 --> 00:14:07.530
It's so pretty!

188
00:14:07.530 --> 00:14:10.060
We can look at the lights later.

189
00:14:10.060 --> 00:14:12.750
Hotaru-chan, aren't you hungry?

190
00:14:13.470 --> 00:14:14.190
Yeah.

191
00:14:17.060 --> 00:14:18.890
The best part is over here.

192
00:14:21.460 --> 00:14:23.710
Kebab
Sandwiches

193
00:14:21.910 --> 00:14:23.220
Kebabs!

194
00:14:23.710 --> 00:14:25.960
Russian Cuisine

195
00:14:23.710 --> 00:14:25.960
Borscht
Piroshki

196
00:14:24.100 --> 00:14:25.630
Borscht!

197
00:14:25.960 --> 00:14:28.460
Nasi goreng!

198
00:14:28.470 --> 00:14:31.470
Nasi Goreng

199
00:14:28.780 --> 00:14:31.470
Oh wow!

200
00:14:32.930 --> 00:14:34.780
They're doing a Christmas fair right now,

201
00:14:34.780 --> 00:14:37.310
so they have stalls with food from all over.

202
00:14:39.790 --> 00:14:42.310
Sorry this isn't a real restaurant, though.

203
00:14:42.310 --> 00:14:43.740
That's totally okay!

204
00:14:43.740 --> 00:14:46.980
It's my dream to conquer foods
from around the world, so I'm stoked!

205
00:14:47.670 --> 00:14:48.900
I'm glad.

206
00:14:50.030 --> 00:14:51.600
Thank you for the food!

207
00:14:50.030 --> 00:14:51.600
Thank you for the food.

208
00:14:56.090 --> 00:14:58.210
Yum!

209
00:14:58.210 --> 00:15:02.610
Hananoi-kun, try this one too! 
Have a bite! It's super good!

210
00:15:34.970 --> 00:15:36.540
Ah...

211
00:15:36.540 --> 00:15:39.500
Amusement parks are so much fun at night.

212
00:15:39.500 --> 00:15:40.190
Oh.

213
00:15:44.100 --> 00:15:45.130
Wanna skate?

214
00:15:45.130 --> 00:15:48.440
No, I'm not athletic at all,
so that's not happening.

215
00:15:48.860 --> 00:15:53.880
I wanted to be like my little sister once, 
but I crashed as soon as I got in the rink.

216
00:15:53.880 --> 00:15:54.860
Oh...

217
00:15:55.710 --> 00:16:00.510
Hotaru-chan, is it okay if I touch you 
just while we're inside the rink?

218
00:16:03.010 --> 00:16:04.970
Huh? W-Wait...

219
00:16:05.730 --> 00:16:08.230
What?!

220
00:16:08.230 --> 00:16:11.710
No way, no way, no way, 
no way, no way, no way!

221
00:16:11.710 --> 00:16:14.630
It's okay. I've got you.

222
00:16:17.240 --> 00:16:23.220
Slowly, slowly. One, two. One, two.

223
00:16:23.220 --> 00:16:25.000
One, two.

224
00:16:23.480 --> 00:16:25.000
One, two...

225
00:16:25.000 --> 00:16:27.000
One, two...

226
00:16:30.550 --> 00:16:35.530
With your help, I can walk, at least.

227
00:16:35.530 --> 00:16:38.780
You did great. You're really 
getting the hang of it.

228
00:16:42.560 --> 00:16:44.720
Huh? The lights went out.

229
00:16:45.410 --> 00:16:47.320
Must be mechanical trouble.

230
00:16:48.190 --> 00:16:50.810
We should still have half an hour.

231
00:16:50.810 --> 00:16:52.680
Huh? Is it already that late?

232
00:16:53.630 --> 00:16:55.170
Where'd the time go?

233
00:16:56.670 --> 00:16:59.120
Maybe we should head on home too.

234
00:16:59.490 --> 00:17:03.780
Thank you so much for tonight.
This was all new to me, so I had a great time.

235
00:17:04.520 --> 00:17:07.050
I've never had a Christmas like this before.

236
00:17:07.050 --> 00:17:11.320
Next time we hang out,
I'll be the one to escort you, okay?

237
00:17:12.450 --> 00:17:13.920
<i>Oh no!</i>

238
00:17:13.920 --> 00:17:16.970
<i>I still haven't answered him
and I'm already talking about next time!</i>

239
00:17:19.920 --> 00:17:21.730
That's what I mean.

240
00:17:22.090 --> 00:17:22.960
Huh?

241
00:17:24.180 --> 00:17:27.250
Hey, do you want to do one final lap?

242
00:17:27.250 --> 00:17:28.630
S-Sure.

243
00:17:35.470 --> 00:17:37.080
Hananoi-kun...

244
00:17:37.620 --> 00:17:39.570
That's what <i>what</i> means?

245
00:17:41.490 --> 00:17:44.210
It's why I like you.

246
00:17:46.200 --> 00:17:50.990
When I do something for you, 
you try to do something back.

247
00:17:50.990 --> 00:17:55.340
Even when something looks hard, 
you're willing to try it out.

248
00:17:57.660 --> 00:17:58.930
Also...

249
00:18:00.050 --> 00:18:01.840
Th-That's enough.

250
00:18:02.470 --> 00:18:05.970
When you think you did something 
wrong, you apologize for it.

251
00:18:06.690 --> 00:18:11.720
You like food, and when you find something 
delicious, you want to share it.

252
00:18:12.080 --> 00:18:16.110
You don't get jealous of people 
who have things you don't.

253
00:18:16.420 --> 00:18:22.060
B-But that's all... totally normal, isn't it?

254
00:18:27.890 --> 00:18:29.310
It's not.

255
00:18:30.640 --> 00:18:33.530
It isn't normal at all. None of that is.

256
00:18:34.240 --> 00:18:37.390
But because that's just how you are,

257
00:18:38.860 --> 00:18:39.870
every day,

258
00:18:40.470 --> 00:18:42.700
I've started to like you more and more.

259
00:18:46.950 --> 00:18:50.180
Happy birthday, Hotaru-chan.

260
00:18:51.070 --> 00:18:55.530
I hope today turned out
 to be special for you.

261
00:18:57.430 --> 00:19:01.240
H-How did you know it was my birthday?

262
00:19:02.760 --> 00:19:09.100
I'm sorry. It was selfish of me to 
drag you out, but it had to be today.

263
00:19:09.690 --> 00:19:11.320
I wanted you to know

264
00:19:11.890 --> 00:19:17.050
that today is the most 
special day in the world.

265
00:19:17.050 --> 00:19:17.830
Whoa!

266
00:19:25.690 --> 00:19:29.340
H-Hananoi-kun! P-P-Put me down!

267
00:19:28.590 --> 00:19:31.140
Hey, Hotaru-chan, it's dangerous to move—

268
00:19:47.220 --> 00:19:49.790
I guess picking you up might 
have been little cheesy.

269
00:19:50.650 --> 00:19:55.110
But did I make you feel
like a princess tonight?

270
00:19:56.450 --> 00:19:57.720
<i>Oh, I get it.</i>

271
00:19:56.920 --> 00:20:01.430
I want to spend Christmas Eve with you

272
00:19:58.550 --> 00:20:00.840
<i>Hananoi-kun knew from the start</i>

273
00:20:02.320 --> 00:20:06.370
<i>that a birthday for me means Christmas,</i>

274
00:20:07.450 --> 00:20:08.980
<i>and winter vacation...</i>

275
00:20:10.310 --> 00:20:12.310
<i>is my little sister's time to shine.</i>

276
00:20:13.640 --> 00:20:18.260
<i>It's a day that's a little more 
fun and special than normal...</i>

277
00:20:19.310 --> 00:20:20.760
<i>for everyone.</i>

278
00:20:23.590 --> 00:20:24.880
<i>That's not what I mean.</i>

279
00:20:26.900 --> 00:20:29.910
Today is the most special day in the world.

280
00:20:30.700 --> 00:20:32.210
It's <i>your</i> day.

281
00:20:34.250 --> 00:20:35.970
I didn't realize...

282
00:20:36.620 --> 00:20:41.390
<i>Whenever I'm with Hananoi-kun, 
everything feels new.</i>

283
00:20:44.140 --> 00:20:46.390
I guess even a princess can get

284
00:20:47.090 --> 00:20:48.810
a little embarrassed sometimes.

285
00:20:52.360 --> 00:20:53.750
Thank you.

286
00:20:59.090 --> 00:21:03.190
Feeling this special makes me so happy.

287
00:21:04.480 --> 00:21:06.760
<i>I hope it's Hananoi-kun.</i>

288
00:21:08.350 --> 00:21:10.370
<i>If I ever fall in love,</i>

289
00:21:11.380 --> 00:21:13.270
<i>I want it to be with Hananoi-kun.</i>

290
00:22:52.980 --> 00:22:54.520
Thank you for today.

291
00:22:55.030 --> 00:22:57.030
U-Um, Hananoi-kun.

292
00:22:57.030 --> 00:22:57.680
Huh?

293
00:22:58.150 --> 00:23:02.440
Um, I just was thinking about it and...

294
00:23:02.440 --> 00:23:08.640
I-Is it okay if we stay like 
this for a little longer?

295
00:23:11.550 --> 00:23:14.820
I know our trial is supposed to end today,

296
00:23:15.340 --> 00:23:18.940
but I feel like I'm on the verge
 of understanding something.

297
00:23:23.110 --> 00:23:24.040
Sure.

298
00:23:24.860 --> 00:23:29.460
If you think you need more time, 
I'll wait as long as you want.

299
00:23:28.510 --> 00:23:33.510
